---
title: Greek Pork & Crushed Lemon Potatoes with Herbed Yoghurt Sauce
description: These lemony, buttery potatoes were eaten by the bowlful in the test kitchen – there’s something unique and comforting about the combination of fluffy spuds coated in all that flavour. On the side of herby pork mixture plus a crisp green salad, this hearty meal tastes like a deconstructed pork souvlaki – or even better!
